{"tid":550921,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一首對自己有特別意義嘅歌","createTime":"2018-02-05T07:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T08:42:01.000Z","uid":72209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"124b1d93505f6ad9a49efa89ca6604c2d4abe55e","tid":550921,"uid":72209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"盧巧音《一念天堂》，<br />\n「原來為你痴 因我太自私<br />\n戀愛這玩意 為了我好天知我知」<br />\n苦戀一場之後自己好耐都走唔出抑鬱，<br />\n聽完呢首歌個人舒服咗好多。<br />\n原來自己對一個人嘅愛都只係出於自私，<br />\n唔需要再為人地唔愛我而咁唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a09ff6870b80a6e285e5b16b92f9c1001e60d0","tid":550921,"uid":74262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de42c397dfdc1beac5354ff845d86648bf2867fb","tid":550921,"uid":143686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:11:34.000Z","msg":"葡萄成熟時<br />\n<br />\n因為我想做既野 或者咁講 我既理想仲離我好遠 但始終都要比啲耐性 我相信有幾成付出就有幾成收獲 好期待我粒葡萄成熟果刻"},{"pid":"88307aef07b11b0c572fbe8dd668efe47dc2bf58","tid":550921,"uid":35193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:12:58.000Z","msg":"由零開始"},{"pid":"04261dd209c210c95da48d6dff89474f96df0580","tid":550921,"uid":147502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:15:14.000Z","msg":"林保怡-心中有數<br />\n這樣用力逃避一種眼神<br />\n其實你己敗露<br />\n不靠著情報<br />\n你心虛我知道"},{"pid":"f836543caa0dea8ff6895bf10ca68e57b0021e58","tid":550921,"uid":149151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:42:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}